text: One of my favourite places to visit whenever I’m in the area. Friendly shop assistant and affordable electronics accessories. I buy all my earphones from them!

Friendly atmosphere. They selling On the go foods, stationary items, soft drinks, snacks etc. For emergency purposes they selling slippers, umbrella, socks also.Maintain cleanliness and very economical 👍🏻👌🏻
Mini Mart… open at hours no one wants. Pointless.
